quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  25,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  25,1,woh ( khuday-e izzojal ) bohat hi babarkat hai jis ne apne bande par quran nazil farmaya taakay ahal haal ko hadaayat kere
  25,2,wohi ke aasman aur zameen ki badshahi isi ki hai aur jis ne ( kisi ko ) beta nahi banaya aur jis ka badshahi mein koi shareek nahi aur jis ne har cheez ko pedakiya aur phir is ka aik andaza thehraya
  25,3,aur ( logon ne ) is ke siwa aur mabood bana liye hain jo koi cheez bhi peda nahi kar saktay aur khud peda kiye gay hain. aur nah apne nuqsaan aur naffa ka kuch ikhtiyar rakhtay hain aur nah marna un ke ikhtiyar mein hai aur nah jeena aur nah mar kar aُth kharray hona
  25,4,aur kafir kehte hain ke yeh ( quran ) mann gharat baatein hi jo is ( mudai risalat ) ne banali hain. aur logon ne is mein is ki madad ki hai. yeh log ( aisa kehnay se ) zulm aur jhoot par ( utar ) aeye hain
  25,5,aur kehte hain ke yeh pehlay logon ki kahaniyan hain jis ko is ne likh rakha hai aur woh subah vsham is ko parh parh kar sunai jati hain
  25,6,keh do ke uss ne uss ko utaara hai jo asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baton ko jaanta hai. be shak woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  25,7,aur kehte hain ke yeh kaisa paighambar hai ke khata hai aur baazaaron mein chalta phirta hai. kyun nazil nahikiya gaya is ke paas koi farishta is ke sath hadaayat karne ko rehta
  25,8,ya is ki taraf ( aasman se ) khazana utaara jata ya is ka koi baagh hota ke is mein khaya karta. aur zalim kehte hain ke tum to aik jaadoo zada shakhs ki pairwi karte ho
  25,9,( ae paighambar ) dekho to yeh tumahray baray mein kis kis terhan ki baatein karte hain so gumraah hogaye aur rasta nahi paskte
  25,10,woh ( khuda ) bohat babarkat hai jo agar chahay to tumahray liye is se behtar ( cheezein ) bana day ( yani ) baagaat jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hon. neez tumahray liye mehal banade
  25,11,balkay yeh to qayamat hi ko jutlatay hain aur hum ne qayamat ke jhutlanay walon ke liye dozakh tayyar kar rakhi hai
  25,12,jis waqt woh un ko daur se dekhe gi ( to ghazabnak ho rahi hogi aur yeh ) is ke josh ( ghazab ) aur cheekhnay chalanay ko sunen ge
  25,13,aur jab yeh dozakh ki kisi tang jagah mein ( zanjeeroon mein ) jakar kar daaley jayen ge to wahan mout ko pukaarain ge
  25,14,aaj aik hi mout ko nah poukaro bohat si mouton ko poukaro
  25,15,pucho ke yeh behtar hai ya bahisht javedani jis ka parhaiz garon se wada hai. yeh un ( ke amlon ) ka badla aur rehne ka thikana hoga
  25,16,wahan jo chahain ge un ke liye muyassar hoga hamesha is mein rahen ge. yeh wada khuda ko ( poora karna ) lazim hai aur is Laiq hai ke maang liya jaye
  25,17,aur jis din ( khuda ) un ko aur unn ko jinhein yeh khuda ke siwa pujte hain jama kere ga to farmaiye gakiya tum ne mere un bundon ko gumraahkiya tha ya yeh khud gumraah hogaye they
  25,18,woh kahin ge to pak hai hamein yeh baat Shayan nah thi ke tairay siwa ouron ko dost banatay. lekin to ne hi un ko aur un ke baap dada ko baratnay ko naematain den yahan taq ke woh teri yaad ko bhool gay. aur yeh halaak honay walay log they
  25,19,to ( kafroo ) unhon ne to tum ko tumhari baat mein jhutla diya. pas ( ab ) tum ( azaab ko ) nah phair satke ho. nah ( kisi se ) madad le satke ho. aur jo shakhs tum mein se zulm kere ga hum is ko barray azaab ka maza chkhayin ge
  25,20,aur hum ne tum se pehlay jitne paighambar beje hain sab khana khatay they aur baazaaron mein chaltay phirtay they. aur hum ne tumhe aik dosray ke liye azmaish banaya hai.kiya tum sabr karo ge. aur tumhara perwar-digaar to dekhnay wala hai
  25,21,aur jo log hum se milnay ki umeed nahi rakhtay. kehte hain ke hum par farishtay kyun nah nazil kiye gay. ya hum apni aankhh se apne perwar-digaar ko dekh len. yeh apne khayaal mein barayi rakhtay hain aur ( isi bana par ) barray sarkash ho rahay hi
  25,22,jis din yeh firshton ko dekhen ge is din gunahgaaron ke liye khusi ki baat nahi hogi aur kahin ge ( khuda kere tum ) rok liye ( aur band kardiye ) jao
  25,23,aur jo unhon ne amal kiye hon ge hum un ki taraf mutwajjah hon ge to un ko urti khaak kar dein ge
  25,24,is din ahal jannat ka thikana bhi behtar hoga aur maqam istirahat bhi hoga
  25,25,aur jis din aasman abr ke sath phatt jaye ga aur farishtay nazil kiye jayen ge
  25,26,is din sachhi badshahi khuda hi ki hogi. aur woh din kafiroon par ( sakht ) mushkil hoga
  25,27,aur jis din ( na aaqbat andesh ) zalim apne haath kaat kaat kar khaye ga ( aur kahe ga ) ke ae kash mein ne paighambar ke sath rishta ikhtiyarkiya hota
  25,28,haae shamat kash mein ne falan shakhs ko dost nah banaya hota
  25,29,is ne mujh ko ( kitaab ) nasiyaat ke mere paas anay ke baad behka diya. aur shetan ensaan ko waqt par dagha dainay wala hai
  25,30,aur paighambar kahin ge ke ae perwar-digaar meri qoum ne is quran ko chore rakha tha
  25,31,aur isi terhan hum ne gunahgaaron mein se har paighambar ka dushman bana diya. aur tumhara perwar-digaar hadaayat dainay aur madad karne ko kaafi hai
  25,32,aur kafir kehte hain ke is par quran aik hi dafaa kyun nahi utaara gaya. is terhan ( aahista aahista ) is liye utaara gaya ke is se tumahray dil ko qaim rakhen. aur isi wastay hum is ko thehr thehr kar parhte rahay hain
  25,33,aur yeh log tumahray paas jo ( aitraaz ki ) baat laatay hain hum tumahray paas is ka maqool aur khoob musharrah jawab bhaij dete hain
  25,34,jo log apne monhon ke bil dozakh ki taraf jama kiye jayen ge un ka thikana bhi bura hai aur woh raste se bhi behke hue hain
  25,35,aur hum ne moose ko kitaab di aur un ke bhai Haroon ko madadgaar bana kar un ke sathkiya
  25,36,aur kaha ke dono un logon ke paas jao jin logon ne hamari ayaton ki takzieeb ki. ( jab takzieeb par uray rahay ) to hum ne un ko halaak kar dala
  25,37,aur Nooh ki qoum ne bhi jab payghambaroon ko jhtlaya to hum ne inhen ghark kar dala aur logon ke liye nishani bana diya. aur zaalmon ke liye hum ne dukh dainay wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  25,38,aur Aad aur smod aur kunwein walon aur un ke darmain aur bohat si jamaaton ko bhi ( halaak kar dala )
  25,39,aur sab ke ( samjhane ke liye ) hum ne misalein bayan kee aur ( nah maan-ne par ) sab ka tehass nehass kardiya
  25,40,aur yeh kafir is bastii par bhi guzar chuke hain jis par buri terhan ka meen barsaya gaya tha.kiya woh is ko dekhte nah hon ge. balkay un ko ( marnay ke baad ) jee utney ki umeed hi nahi thi .
  25,41,aur yeh log jab tum ko dekhte hain to tumhari hansi uratye hain. kekiya yahi shakhs hai jis ko khuda ne paighambar bana kar bheja hai
  25,42,agar hum ne apne mabodon ke baray mein saabit qadam nah rehtay to yeh zaroor hum ko behka deta. ( aur un se phair deta ) aur yeh anqareeb maloom karlen ge jab azaab dekhen ge ke seedhay raste se kon bhatka howa hai
  25,43,kiya tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jis ne khwahish nafs ko mabood bana rakha hai tokiya tum is par nigehbaan ho saktay ho
  25,44,ya tum yeh khayaal karte ho ke un mein aksar suntay ya samajte hain ( nahi ) yeh to chopaiyon ki terhan hain balkay un se bhi ziyada gumraah hain
  25,45,balkay tum ne apne perwar-digaar ( ki qudrat ) ko nahi dekha ke woh saaye ko kis terhan daraaz kar ( ke phela ) deta hai. aur agar woh chahta to is ko ( be harkat )tehra rakhta phir Sooraj ko is ka rehnuma bana deta hai
  25,46,phir is ko hum aahista aahista apni taraf samaitt letay hain
  25,47,aur wohi to hai jis ne raat ko tumahray liye parda aur neend ko aaraam banaya aur din ko aُth kharray honay ka waqt thehraya
  25,48,aur wohi to hai jo apni rehmat kemeinhہ ke agay hawaon ko khush khaberi bana kar bhejta hai. aur hum aasman se pak ( aur nthra howa ) pani barastee hain
  25,49,taakay is se shehar murda ( yani zameen aftada ) ko zindah kar dein aur phir usay bohat se chopaiyon aur admion ko jo hum ne peda kiye hain pilate hain
  25,50,aur hum ne is ( quran ki ayaton ) ko terhan terhan se logon mein bayankiya taakay nasiyaat pakren magar bohat se logon ne inkaar ke siwa qubool nahkiya
  25,51,aur agar hum chahtay to har bastii mein darane wala bhaij dete
  25,52,to tum kafiroon ka kaha nah manu aur un se is quran ke hukum ke mutabiq barray shdomd se lrho
  25,53,aur wohi to hai jis ne do daryaaon ko mila diya aik ka pani sheree hai pyaas bujhanay wala aur dosray ka khaari chhaati jalanay wala. aur dono ke darmain aik aarr aur mazboot oot bana di
  25,54,aur wohi to hai jis ne pani se aadmi pedakiya. phir is ko sahib nasb aur sahib qaraabat دامادی banaya. aur tumhara perwar-digaar ( har terhan ki ) qudrat rakhta hai
  25,55,aur yeh log khuda ko chore kar aisi cheez ki parastish kar te hain jo nah un ko faida pouncha sakay aur nah zarrar. aur kafir apne perwar-digaar ki mukhalfat mein bara zor maarta hai
  25,56,aur hum ne ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum ko sirf khusi aur azaab ki khabar sunanay ko bheja hai
  25,57,"keh do ke mein tum se is ( kaam ) ki ujrat nahi mangta, haan jo shakhs chahay apne perwar-digaar ki taraf jaane ka rasta ikhtiyar kere"
  25,58,aur is ( khuday-e ) zindah par bharosa rakho jo ( kabhi ) nahi marey ga aur is ki tareef ke sath tasbeeh karte raho. aur woh apne bundon ke gunaaho se khabar rakhnay ko kaafi hai
  25,59,jis ne asmano aur zameen ko aur jo kuch un dono ke darmain hai chay din mein pedakiya phir arsh par ja thehra woh ( jis ka naam ) rehman ( yani bara meharban hai ) to is ka haal kisi bakhabar se daryaft karlo
  25,60,aur jab un ( kufar ) se kaha jata hai ke rehman ko sajda karo to kehte hain rehmankiya?kiya jis ke liye tum hum se kehte ho hum is ke agay sajda karen aur is se bidaktay hain
  25,61,aur ( khuda ) barri barket wala hai jis ne asmano mein burj banaye aur un mein ( aftaab ka nihayat roshan ) chairag aur chamakta howa chaand bhi banaya
  25,62,aur wohi to hai jis ne raat aur din ko aik dosray ke peechay anay jaane wala banaya. ( yeh baatein ) is shakhs ke liye jo ghhor karna chahay ya shkrgzari ka iradah kere ( sochnay aur samajhney ki hain )
  25,63,aur khuda ke bande to woh hain jo zameen par ahistagi se chaltay hain aur jab jaahil log un se ( jahilana ) guftagu karte hain to salam kehte hain
  25,64,aur jo woh apne perwar-digaar ke agay sjday karkay aur ( ijaz vadb se ) kharray reh kar raatain busr karte hain
  25,65,aur jo dua mangte rehtay hain ke ae perwar-digaar dozakh ke azaab ko hum se daur rakiyo ke is ka azaab barri takleef ki cheez hai
  25,66,aur dozakh tehrnay aur rehne ki bohat buri jagah hai
  25,67,aur woh jab kharch karte hain to nah be ja uratye hain aur nah tangi ko kaam mein laatay hain balkay aitdaal ke sath. nah zaroorat se ziyada nah kam
  25,68,aur woh jo khuda ke sath kisi aur mabood ko nahi pkarte aur jin jandaar ko maar daalna khuda ne haraamkiya hai is ko qatal nahi karte magar jaaiz tareeq par ( yani Shariat ke mutabiq ) aur badkaari nahi karte. aur jo yeh kaam kere ga sakht gunah mein mubtala hoga
  25,69,qayamat ke din is ko dona azaab hoga aur zillat o khawari se hamesha is mein rahay ga
  25,70,magar jis ne tauba ki aur imaan laya aur achay kaam kiye to aisay logon ke gunaaho ko khuda nakiyon se badal day ga. aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  25,71,aur jo tauba karta aur amal naik karta hai to be shak woh khuda ki taraf rujoo karta hai
  25,72,aur woh jo jhooti gawahi nahi dete aur jab un ko behooda cheezon ke paas se guzarnay ka ittafaq ho to buzurgana andaaz se guzarte hain
  25,73,aur woh ke jab un ko perwar-digaar ki baatein samjhai jati hain to unn par andhay aur behray ho kar nahi girtay ( balkay ghhor se suntay hain )
  25,74,aur woh jo ( khuda se ) dua mangte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko hamari biwion ki taraf se ( dil ka chain ) aur aulaad ki taraf se aankhh ki thandak ataa farma aur hamein parhaiz garon ka imam bana
  25,75,un ( sifaat ke ) logon ko un ke sabr ke badlay ounchay ounchay mehal diye jayen ge. aur wahan farishtay un se dua o slaam ke sath mulaqaat karen ge
  25,76,is mein woh hamesha rahen ge. aur woh tehrnay aur rehne ki bohat hi umdah jagah hai
  25,77,keh do ke agar tum ( khuda ko ) nahi pkarte to mera perwar-digaar bhi tumhari kuch parwa nahi karta. tum ne takzieeb ki hai so is ki saza ( tumahray liye ) lazim hogi
